"body":"Related to #1969.\r\n\r\nThe following should work, but Psalm doesn't take note of the `$Foo instanceof $fooClass` when `$fooClass` is generic.\r\n\r\n```php\r\n<?php\r\n\r\ninterface Foo {}\r\n\r\nfinal class FooStorage\r\n{\r\n    /** @var array<class-string<Foo>, Foo> */\r\n    private $storage = [];\r\n  \r\n    /**\r\n     * @template T as Foo\r\n     * @template-typeof T $fooClass\r\n     * @param class-string<T> $fooClass\r\n     * @return T|null\r\n     */\r\n    public function get($fooClass)\r\n    {\r\n        if (isset($this->storage[$fooClass])) {\r\n            $Foo = $this->storage[$fooClass];\r\n\r\n            if ($Foo instanceof $fooClass) {\r\n                return $Foo;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        return null;\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nPsalm output (using commit 352f18b): \r\n```\r\nERROR: InvalidReturnStatement - 22:21 - The type 'Foo' does not match the declared return type 'T as Foo|null' for FooStorage::get\r\n\r\nERROR: InvalidReturnType - 14:16 - The declared return type 'T|null' for FooStorage::get is incorrect, got 'null|Foo'\r\n```\r\n\r\nhttps://psalm.dev/r/a416e4534f","closed_by":{"login":"muglug","id":2292638,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyOTI2Mzg=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2292638?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug","html_url":"https://github.com/muglug","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/received_events",